data.title: Bookmobile Special Visit: Clover Bar Pioneer Court
data.meta_description: In addition to the regular weekly schedule, the Bookmobile visits senior's lodges, complexes and apartments throughout Strathcona County every three weeks. Clover Bar Pioneer Lodge is at 6 Mission Street, Sherwood Park.
